hand von vier Parametern systematische Antworten auf die Frage liefert, warum welcher Marker bevorzugt in welchen Kontexten auftritt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexCausative. 0aGerman languagexVariation. 4aKausale Konjunktion. 4aKorpus ‹Linguistik›. 4aLinguistik. 4aMerkmal. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aCausal markers.  aConnectors.1 aFrohning, Dagmar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2007z9783110277135oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2007z9783110276909oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978348430516840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311096934440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110969344423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110969344/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2007  aZDB-23-DGGb2007  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014